{"tid":1135852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟講下點樣捱過低潮期","createTime":"2019-05-02T14:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T15:19:47.000Z","uid":44754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c655f748afcbcbe52beb5f804f011f60a43152ff","tid":1135852,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"我拋磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年前 工作上俾老細調咗去第2 team<br />\n自此俾人投閒置散 阿頭只會肯用自己人 我呢啲被歸邊嘅只係負責垃圾project<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶 差唔多調team嘅同一時間俾人飛咗 呢家周不時都會夢見佢 不過人哋已經有拖拍 剩低我on99<br />\n<br />\n工作唔順利 好自然就去搵工<br />\n結果因為學歷低無人請<br />\n所以下個學年我決定讀返書<br />\n拎返個學歷<br />\n呢家日日同自己講<br />\n捱多3個月就可以辭職 重新出發<br />\n溝學生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個人仲係經常情緒低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70af965c1fc765555356345951cb60479a685199","tid":1135852,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"讀咩"},{"pid":"ac8bc0736dd8b537aaee2d5b6b5796b6ce16dfa9","tid":1135852,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲"},{"pid":"65fdf4070bcf88922cafca6cde22209afe2da6dd","tid":1135852,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70af965c1fc765555356345951cb60479a685199","tid":1135852,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"讀咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:13:49.000Z","msg":"中文系學士"},{"pid":"3347ff0cb7766306e23a95a4545818f42508919a","tid":1135852,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac8bc0736dd8b537aaee2d5b6b5796b6ce16dfa9","tid":1135852,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"今年24"},{"pid":"4735e16ad24bae439b95b90f8918158cc7e0fe0e","tid":1135852,"uid":162295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc